{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2803358, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实非暴力、不合作中间加个标点符号比较好…", "timestamp": 1635302494, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2803367, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": 2803358, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那么对应的：非必要，不出校；加了标点感觉难道更像条件结构了吗。。。", "timestamp": 1635302671, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2803376, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": 2803367, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我个人的语感是，非…不…就是个条件结构，比如非礼勿视、非请勿进", "timestamp": 1635302812, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2803420, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我第一次见到「非暴力不合作」确实理解成了「除非使用暴力，否则不合作」。只能说这句话是不符合语言习惯的。", "timestamp": 1635303292, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2803436, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "非暴力是一个整体？非必要的非是表否定？", "timestamp": 1635303469, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2803438, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": 2803420, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 我也，当时还很好奇", "timestamp": 1635303495, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2803960, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "非暴力，不合作，指的是不用暴力而且不和殖民者合作。这两个是并列关系，不是逻辑关系", "timestamp": 1635309787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2804098, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "非必要不出校是省略句", "timestamp": 1635311653, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2811295, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 533922, "reply_to": 2803960, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 有道理啊，这样一说就不觉得非暴力不合作变扭了", "timestamp": 1635401829, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 533922, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "非必要不出校 这句话到底应该怎么理解？\n非暴力不合作 这句话呢？\n\n二者语法上有啥区别吗？必要和暴力都是形容词，出校和合作都是动词，按说结构完全一样啊。\n\n为啥前者被理解为条件结构，后者被理解为副词修饰动词的结构呢。", "timestamp": 1635302338, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1635401829, "url": "", "vote": {}}}